END-TO-END FLOW:
===============


1. Collect metrics (CPU, Memory, Disk, Processes)
2. Store metrics вҶ’ JSON (history layer)
3. Build structured prompt
4. Send to AI Core (/generate)
5. Retrieve RAG context (vector DB)
6. Combine вҶ’ Final prompt
7. LLM generates insight
8. Output returned to user


